      "writtenOn": "2019-06-13T19:11:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There\u0027s a race condition here, if the video stops playing at the same time changePlayConfig is called.\n\nThread 1: Checks isRunning() -\u003e true\nThread 2: Exits out of play() loop.\nThread 1: Calls changePlayConfig(true), setting mLooping to true\n\nSince the thread has already exited, the video doesn\u0027t loop.  I think the functionality to play/restart should be within the start function under lock, or make it so that we can\u0027t change the looping parameter while the video is playing.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 147,
        "startChar": 16,
        "endLine": 152,
        "endChar": 17
      },
      "revId": "b9de8fd5bde897bcd57cb2a6cac2b01dafb9a9cf",
